volumes.title: OutFox Serenity Volume 1
volumes.description: Released August 27, 2021, Serenity Volume I is the first installment of the OutFox Serenity project, the official community simfile pack of Project OutFox. It features music by Aspid Cat, Drazil, Jack5, Matduke, mmry, Daniel Rotwind, Seo, and Sevish. Alongside 4-panel (dance) and 5-panel (pump) charts, some of its songs also have Be-Mu, Po-Mu, techno (8- and 9-panel), gddm, and gdgf, and gh charts.

volumes.title: OutFox Serenity Volume 1 Winter Update
volumes.description: The Winter Update (version 1.5) adds three new songs by DJ Megas, Matduke and Pekoneko (ペコネコ), keysounded versions of selected songs for be-mu, po-mu, and gh mode, as well as more new charts—including Serenity's first ez2 (simulating ez2Dancer), maniax (simulating Dance ManiaX), and smx charts.

volumes.title: OutFox Serenity Volume 2
volumes.description: Released September 4, 2022, Serenity Volume II features music by Ace of Beat, Finite Limit, Jack5, Kurio Prokos, Lagoona, Rilliam, rN, SiLiS, and td. It also features the Serenity debut of ds3ddx and kickbox mode charts.

volumes.title: OutFox Serenity Volume 2 Winter Update
volumes.description: Released February 21, 2023, the Winter Update (version 2.5) adds three new songs by Akako Hinami and Zenth, as well as new charts for other songs from previous versions.
